3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper presents an approach to solving a computer vision problem using machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video sequences and image matching. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper uses neural networks for solving the problem of image matching.
